title: Races I've competed in
name: Races I've competed in
description:
A Map by Tswicegood

A list of places that I've raced mountain or road bikes.

properties.name: 2002 Chupacabras 100km
properties.description: Posted by Tswicegood2003 ChupacapbrasFirst race I ever competed in. Finished in the top 250, and didn\'t get passed in the final 1/3rd of the race.

properties.name: 2003 Chupacabras 100km
properties.description: Posted by Tswicegood2003 ChupacapbrasSecond time at the Chupa - finished 46th out over over 2,000 starters. Competed on the second place team.

properties.name: 2006 Coyote Classic
properties.description: Posted by TswicegoodEl Paso, TX2006 Coyote Classic at Franklin Mountain State Park. Took 2nd in the 19 - 29 Pro/Expert. First was a a semi-pro.

properties.name: 2006 Dawn 'til Dusk Race
properties.description: Posted by TswicegoodGallup, NM12 hour co-ed duo with S - took 3rd place even though she only put in 2 of our 8 laps.

properties.name: 2006 Deer Valley NMBS Marathon
properties.description: Posted by TswicegoodRaced the 19 - 29 Marathon race and won. Second national win of the season at my second national race.

properties.name: 2006 High Altitude Classic
properties.description: Posted by Tswicegood3rd race of the NMORS, 2nd that I competed in. Took 3rd in the 19 - 29 Pro/Expert. First was the same semi-pro that beat me in El Paso. The altitude really got to me, started getting dizzy on the third lap.

properties.name: 2006 La Tierra Torture
properties.description: Posted by TswicegoodThe course that owned me this year. La Tierra in Santa Fe was sandy, hot, and chewed me up and spit me out. Bad, bad race. Only race of the year that Damian lapped me.

properties.name: 2006 New Mexico State Championship - Horny Toad Hustle
properties.description: Posted by TswicegoodThe NM State Campionship and stop #9 on the NMORS series. One the race, but didn\'t really put in a hard effort because I wasn\'t racing against anyone.

properties.name: 2006 Nova Marathon
properties.description: Posted by TswicegoodFountain Hills, AZThe opener to the 2006 NMBS marathon races

properties.name: 2006 USA National Mountain Bike Championship
properties.description: Posted by TswicegoodRaced in the 2006 USA National Championship 19 - 29 Marathon. Took 3rd place.

properties.name: 2006 Whiskey Off Road
properties.description: Posted by TswicegoodPrescott, AZThe 2006 Whiskey Off-Road 50 Proof. Pulled 29th place out of 107 finishers.
